@wxing1292 @yiminc 
Do we really only want do this for workflow ID only? Or should we expand the field size for all governed by this check and hard code the max to 1000?

The dynamic config override covers the following:
```
	// MaxIDLengthLimit is the length limit for various IDs, including: Namespace, TaskQueue, WorkflowID, ActivityID, TimerID,
	// WorkflowType, ActivityType, SignalName, MarkerName, ErrorReason/FailureReason/CancelCause, Identity, RequestID
```
 
https://github.com/temporalio/temporal/blob/4c212e5bb48fe270f35dea96bc0bdd0b9ed746d1/common/dynamicconfig/constants.go#L133
